      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 1947: loadMissingBodyOverwrites() transforms every loaded TEXT commit without checking whether it is an edition commit or a visible parent message, then emits one update per transformed commit. On large histories this can synchronously call plugin code hundreds/thousands of times immediately after loading, which is expensive and can flood SwarmMessageUpdated signals. Batch messages into a single transform call and emit at most one update per affected parent message.\n```suggestion\nstd::vector\u003clibjami::SwarmMessage\u003e batch;\n// collect snapshots\npluginChatManager.transformSwarmMessages(batch, accountId_, convId);\n// write results back and collect unique parent ids to signal once\n```",
